      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been so well-loved and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable, smooth drive without any of the stress. It\u2019s served me great and still has plenty of life left for its next owner. If you're looking for a dependable car that looks awesome on the road, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take it for a spin!",
