    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis maintains its composure with aluminum multi-link rear geometry and updated bushings. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS inspection and fresh throttle body actuators to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. While showing signs of spirited use, the hydraulic steering remains communicative and the rod bearings have been serviced proactively. A mechanically sound example of Bavarian engineering ready for the apex.",
